column5: Out hunting with the pup today and came across this plate. TROUT A In the area of a steelhead honey hole!!!! Looks like their rig took a beating trying to get out of the mud they were stuck in LOL.
stuff disturber  That came out wrong,,,,,,,,Nope,filter worked.LOL
Miracon's friend trying to get rid of the raccoon!
lol... Odd how I am permanently linked to the aurora now, even though I never caught one and everyone else has.
I'd be lookin' for the trout that coughed that plate up    And I'd clean him for free....
Figures.I loss three plates from wheeling and it's not mine.
